285
00:10:12,025 --> 00:10:13,095
(sultry chuckle)

286
00:10:13,095 --> 00:10:15,021
Lucifer...

287
00:10:15,022 --> 00:10:17,008
Ah! Speak of the me.

288
00:10:17,008 --> 00:10:19,025
Out here. Now.

289
00:10:24,046 --> 00:10:25,076
What did you do?

290
00:10:25,076 --> 00:10:27,023
