in your pants. What...?

295
00:10:36,037 --> 00:10:37,097
Are you
even listening to me?

296
00:10:37,097 --> 00:10:39,027
Not really. Look.

297
00:10:39,027 --> 00:10:41,051
A new doctor's moved in.

298
00:10:41,051 --> 00:10:43,078
Dr. Canaan.

299
00:10:43,078 --> 00:10:45,051
How Biblical.

300
00:10:45,051 --> 00:10:47,098
Sure, let's add another
random doctor to the case.

301
00:10:47,098 --> 00:10:49,038
Great idea.

302
00:10:49,038 --> 00:10:52,085
Now, look, I assure you,
Dr. Martin is excellent.

303
00:10:52,085 --> 00:10:54,095
She trained at Stanford,
she lectures at USC,

304
00:10:54,096 --> 00:10:56,035
