347
00:12:13,050 --> 00:12:14,097
Yeah.

348
00:12:14,097 --> 00:12:16,007
Top work, Sherlock.

349
00:12:17,050 --> 00:12:19,094
(sighs)

350
00:12:21,021 --> 00:12:22,097
 So I don't understand

