never that easy.

355
00:12:29,052 --> 00:12:31,062
Well, it is for me.

356
00:12:31,062 --> 00:12:33,062
Usually.

357
00:12:35,099 --> 00:12:37,049
I, uh, I may have
overstepped

358
00:12:37,049 --> 00:12:39,062
