365
00:12:54,007 --> 00:12:56,014
But lately something's changed.

366
00:12:56,014 --> 00:12:58,051
He... he makes time for me.

367
00:12:58,051 --> 00:13:00,065
He makes time for us.

368
00:13:00,065 --> 00:13:03,011
He's really putting
in an effort.

369
00:13:03,012 --> 00:13:05,045
Yes, if ever anyone
deserved

370
00:13:05,045 --> 00:13:08,002
