it's Dan.

371
00:13:14,039 --> 00:13:16,039
(phone ringing)

372
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:19,046
Decker.

373
00:13:19,047 --> 00:13:20,057
LINDA:
Uh, hello, Detective.

374
00:13:20,057 --> 00:13:21,060
It's about Richard.

375
00:13:21,060 --> 00:13:22,063
I wanted to warn you.

376
00:13:22,064 --> 00:13:24,014
He may be unstable.

377
00:13:24,014 --> 00:13:25,064
Possibly dangerous.

378
00:13:25,064 --> 00:13:27,021
I'll handle it,
but thanks.

379
00:13:27,021 --> 00:13:28,044
I don't mean to you.

380
00:13:28,044 --> 00:13:29,091
I mean to himself.

381
00:13:29,091 --> 00:13:31,028
(siren whoops)

382
00:13:31,028 --> 00:13:32,044
