383
00:13:32,045 --> 00:13:34,065
Yeah, you may be right.

384
00:13:34,065 --> 00:13:36,028
Lucifer?

385
00:13:36,028 --> 00:13:37,092
Oh, my God.

386
00:13:37,092 --> 00:13:39,002
There's another one.

387
00:13:39,002 --> 00:13:40,018
LUCIFER:
Hey, Detective!

388
00:13:40,019 --> 00:13:42,099
You need your roots done!

389
00:13:49,020 --> 00:13:51,010
(crowd chattering)

390
00:13:51,010 --> 00:13:53,003
MAN: What is he doing?

391
00:13:53,003 --> 00:13:54,033
I've made up my mind.

392
00:13:54,033 --> 00:13:56,047
You can't stop me.

393
00:13:56,047 --> 00:13:58,034
What? Oh, no.
I'm not here to stop you.

394
00:13:58,034 --> 00:13:59,094
If you want to jump,
go for it.

395
00:14:01,031 --> 00:14:04,024
Is this some kind
of reverse psychology?

396
00:14:04,024 --> 00:14:05,044
No, quite serious.

397
00:14:05,045 --> 00:14:06,048
Go for it.

