Pull me back up!

410
00:14:31,010 --> 00:14:33,024
Pull me up, please!

411
00:14:36,044 --> 00:14:37,071
Oh, God.

412
00:14:37,071 --> 00:14:39,085
I'd save your breath
if I were you.

