00:14:39,085 --> 00:14:41,098
When it comes to this sort
of thing, he's quite judgy.

414
00:14:41,098 --> 00:14:44,062
Right, back to the matter
in hand.

415
00:14:44,062 --> 00:14:47,052
Now, you were so jealous
