418
00:14:51,042 --> 00:14:53,042
I was about to jump,
because he's dead.

419
00:14:53,043 --> 00:14:55,006
Don't fib, Rickster.

420
00:14:55,006 --> 00:14:56,026
I know about
your death threats.

421
00:14:56,026 --> 00:14:59,013
(scoffs)
I was in a bad place.

422
00:14:59,013 --> 00:15:00,053
Kara had just dumped me.

423
00:15:00,053 --> 00:15:02,007
I made my threats.

424
00:15:02,007 --> 00:15:03,040
Then I went to his office...

425
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:05,000
And killed him.

426
00:15:05,001 --> 00:15:06,050
And he talked me down.

427
00:15:06,051 --> 00:15:09,004
And afterwards,
he kept seeing me,

428
00:15:09,004 --> 00:15:11,048
