I couldn't afford to pay him.

429
00:15:11,048 --> 00:15:14,001
I mean, he'd got me
through my divorce, bankruptcy,

430
00:15:14,001 --> 00:15:15,045
the death of my parrot.

431
00:15:15,045 --> 00:15:17,055
Oh, I've just realized

432
00:15:17,055 --> 00:15:19,025
you're not jealous,
