434
00:15:21,002 --> 00:15:22,075
Pathetic, really.

435
00:15:22,076 --> 00:15:25,002
(sighs) Well, if you can't
tell me what I need to know,

436
00:15:25,003 --> 00:15:27,003
what good are you?

437
00:15:27,003 --> 00:15:29,033
