that I have a lot to live for?

438
00:15:29,033 --> 00:15:31,001
Well, I wish
I could, Ricky,

439
00:15:31,001 --> 00:15:32,070
but your life sounds
incredibly bleak.

440
00:15:32,070 --> 00:15:35,040
Ironically, it seems there's
nowhere to go but up.

441
00:15:37,024 --> 00:15:40,010
(sighs)

442
00:15:40,011 --> 00:15:41,044
You know what? You're right.

443
00:15:41,044 --> 00:15:43,007
Hmm?

444
00:15:43,008 --> 00:15:45,058
Maybe the worst is behind me.

445
00:15:45,058 --> 00:15:47,038
Hmm.

446
00:15:47,038 --> 00:15:49,025
I think I'm ready
to go in now.

447
00:15:49,025 --> 00:15:50,072
Well, I wasn't asking,
but, uh,

