00:16:01,073 --> 00:16:05,033
All right, Richard, we confirmed
your alibi with your neighbor.

454
00:16:05,033 --> 00:16:06,073
You're free to go.

455
00:16:06,073 --> 00:16:08,053
How did this happen?

456
00:16:08,054 --> 00:16:10,020
Poor Sandy.

457
00:16:10,020 --> 00:16:11,014
