00:16:18,078 --> 00:16:21,075
Yes, how open was
his relationship therapy, hmm?

462
00:16:21,075 --> 00:16:24,022
No, it's nothing like that.

463
00:16:24,022 --> 00:16:25,068
That's just
how the Shaws are.

464
00:16:25,069 --> 00:16:28,059
