495
00:17:43,036 --> 00:17:44,086
Interesting.

496
00:17:44,086 --> 00:17:46,030
What?

497
00:17:46,030 --> 00:17:47,067
Well, I find people
who are rude

498
00:17:47,067 --> 00:17:49,083
