503
00:17:58,088 --> 00:18:00,071
LUCIFER:
Doctor?

504
00:18:00,071 --> 00:18:03,058
What a surprise.

505
00:18:03,058 --> 00:18:05,038
What are you doing here?

506
00:18:05,039 --> 00:18:06,072
I thought you asked me
to meet you here.

507
00:18:06,072 --> 00:18:08,062
That-that was me.
I felt like

508
00:18:08,062 --> 00:18:11,039
